loaded from their site at http://www.iconfactory.com.How To Use The Extras:Extras vary. Depending on what collection you downloaded, you may have an associated background image or a kaleidoscope theme or something else entirely. Background images may be installed using the Desktop Pictures control panel or other desktop picture application. Kaleidoscope themes must use the kaleidoscope program which may be acquired at http://www.kaleidoscope.net. Contact The Author:At the date specified in this file, I may be reached by sending e-mail to: gipson@mindspring.com which may also be found at the Paurian Café website: http://members.xoom.com/paurian. Because of the changing attributes of the internet and the possibility of e-mail and/or website address change, I can neither guarantee the e-mail nor the site address at the time you are reading this message. Nevertheless, please try.Site Suggestions:The following websites are some which I enjoy. Feel free to give them a try. These sites may change address (or disappear) in time.The Icon Factory          Great Icons for your macintosh desktop          www.iconfactory.comFamily Life                  A site with a mission - Great articles             www.fltoday.comPaurian Café                The Paurian website                                       members.xoom.com/paurianVerse:“...wash and make yourselves clean. Take your evil deeds out of my sight! Stop doing wrong, learn to do right! Seek justice, encourage those whoare oppressed. Defend the cause of the fatherless, plead the case of the widow.Come now, let us reason together,” says the LORD. “Though your sins are like scarlet, they shall be as white as snow; though they are red as crimson, they shall be like wool.”   - Isaiah 1:16-18For more information, please visit the Paurian Café website at:http://members.xoom.com/paurian/soapbox/eternity.html